Package: chaoticds
Type: Package
Title: Chaotic Dynamical Systems Utilities
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Diogo Ribeiro <dfr@esmad.ipp.pt>
Maintainer: Diogo Ribeiro <dfr@esmad.ipp.pt>
Authors@R: c(person("Diogo", "Ribeiro", email = "dfr@esmad.ipp.pt", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-2022-7072")))
Description: Collection of utilities for extreme-value analysis of simple chaotic maps. Includes simulation of logistic and Henon maps and tools for block maxima, peaks-over-threshold (POT) and extremal index estimation. Provides functions for threshold diagnostics, bootstrap confidence intervals, cluster analysis, and mixing condition checks.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/DiogoRibeiro7/chaotic-dynamical-systems
